1. Današnja utakmica je bila velika *pobeda* za naš tim. (Today's game was a big victory for our team.)
2. Moramo da *pobedimo* naše strahove i krenemo napred. (We must overcome our fears and move forward.)
3. Ona je već pet puta odnela *pobedu* na ovom takmičenju. (She has already won five times at this competition.)
4. Ova bitka nije još dobijena, ali mi ćemo *pobediti* na kraju. (This battle is not yet won, but we will prevail in the end.)
5. Treba da se usredsredimo na cilj i ne dozvolimo da nam *pobeda* izmakne iz ruku. (We need to focus on the goal and not let victory slip through our fingers.)